  skillName: "\xC2n O\xE1n"
  skillDescription: "Sau khi b\u1EA1n thu \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c \xEDt nh\u1EA5t hai
    l\xE1 b\xE0i c\xF9ng l\xFAc t\u1EEB m\u1ED9t ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ch\u01A1i kh\xE1c,
    b\u1EA1n c\xF3 th\u1EC3 l\u1EC7nh h\u1ECD r\xFAt m\u1ED9t l\xE1 b\xE0i.\r\nSau
    khi b\u1EA1n nh\u1EADn 1 \u0111i\u1EC3m s\xE1t th\u01B0\u01A1ng, tr\u1EEB khi
    ngu\u1ED3n g\xE2y s\xE1t th\u01B0\u01A1ng giao cho b\u1EA1n m\u1ED9t l\xE1 b\xE0i
    tr\xEAn tay, n\u1EBFu kh\xF4ng th\xEC h\u1ECD gi\u1EA3m 1 \u0111i\u1EC3m sinh
    l\u1EF1c. N\u1EBFu b\xE0i h\u1ECD giao cho b\u1EA1n kh\xF4ng ph\u1EA3i ch\u1EA5t
    \u2665, b\u1EA1n r\xFAt m\u1ED9t l\xE1 b\xE0i."
  urlVoice: []
